{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act16side", "eventName": "吾導先路", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "GA-6", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "安魂曲", "storyInfo": "樓上的塞茜莉亞高唱古老的薩卡茲歌謠，鐘聲轟然鳴響。被稱為“教宗”的老人向薩科塔發問：這是你我的幸運，還是不幸？\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "鐘樓的過道很狹窄，腳下的石階又濕又滑。石頭牆壁很粗糙，摸上去涼涼的......就像那片森林裡的樹。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "腳步聲回蕩在走廊裡，前面會有什麼？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我是薩科塔和薩卡茲的孩子，他們說，我身上寄託著......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我不知道，那是我沒有聽過的音節。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但我記得羅塞菈姐姐的表情。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她雙眼低垂，帶著一點笑容，兩手交疊在一起，彷彿掌中有什麼寶物。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "他們......大家，希望我做什麼呢？到現在，我也沒明白。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但是，我已經明白了，最應該去做的事情，是自己想要做的事。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "薩科塔也好，薩卡茲也好。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我是塞茜莉亞。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "只是塞茜莉亞。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "再見，媽媽......你會看著我嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g11_laterano_alley", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$exciting_intro", "key": "$exciting_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_279_excu_4"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾澤爾，左前方。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔！", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#2$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#2$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好險！", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#2$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說，我們也打不出個結果，要不然算了吧？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_279_excu_4", "name2": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1", "enter": "left", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.4, "xstrength": 0.0, "ystrength": 0.0, "vibrato": 0.0, "randomness": 0.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 100.0, "power": 0.0, "times": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "power": 0.0, "times": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 80.0, "power": 0.0, "times": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.4, "xstrength": 0.0, "ystrength": 0.0, "vibrato": 0.0, "randomness": 0.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......真是完全不聽人說話啊。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#5$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾澤爾，你不是最擔心塞茜莉亞的安危嗎？其實說不定塞茜莉亞在我手裡會更安全哦？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#4$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你以為我會相信嗎？", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#2$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從來不說假話的。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算你說的是真的，塞茜莉亞自己不願意，那就不行！", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#2$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......有時候我真覺得，安多恩給我添了很多麻煩。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#5$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "！！", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_279_excu_4"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要分神，艾澤爾。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不......費德里科前輩！", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#2$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有沒有感覺到......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#2$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#3$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "空氣在顫動。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "middle", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "彷彿有某種東西正從虛無中析出。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "middle", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "那是一股強大而純淨的力量，卻不像是任何已知的源石技藝。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "middle", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "某種古老的結構正被喚醒。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "middle", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "某種遺忘的聲音將要鳴響。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "middle", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_279_excu_4"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾澤爾，行動變更，你去鐘樓確認情況。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_279_excu_4"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個反叛信使交給我。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g4_laterano_cathedralliving", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "教宗閣下，這是！", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#4$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噓——", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薇爾麗芙，關閉中廳，暫停一切會面。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到底發生了什麼？", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的前任，上一代教宗，很喜歡研究歷史，這件事你聽說過嗎？", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......確實沒有。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不怪你，他實在太蹩腳了。他那些文章錯漏百出，讓人不敢恭維。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與其說是在研究歷史，不如說他喜歡把歷史當成材料，盡情發揮他的想像。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他喜歡寫一些相當......浪漫主義的比喻。雖然放在歷史論文裡實在有濫情的嫌疑，但確實能給人留下印象。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他說，“歷史，就是無形的巨人在大地上譜寫的無限多聲部的樂章”。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "照他這個比喻，我們這位巨人音樂家，可能寫到新的一小節了。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "肺裡的空氣被竭盡全力擠壓而出，又被深吸回肺中。"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我絆了一跤，掙扎著爬起來，又向前衝去。"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能清晰感覺到，有什麼東西正在醞釀。"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在鐘樓頂層，就在那扇門之後，就在塞茜莉亞所在的地方。"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "推開門——"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gateopen", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$dignified_intro", "key": "$dignified_loop", "crossfade": 3.0, "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "26_i12", "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "y": 40.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleTo": 0.8, "yScaleTo": 0.8, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "duration": 40.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個瘦弱的女孩在唱歌。"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一首古老的薩卡茲歌謠。"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她唱得如此真摯，嗓音稚嫩，投入了全部的情感。"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只能呆呆站在原地，竭盡全力屏住呼吸，生怕我雜亂的氣息打擾了歌聲的流動。"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在某個瞬間，我突然發現自己什麼也聽不到了。"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯有鐘聲，彷彿跨越亙古而來。"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g4_laterano_cathedralliving", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......鐘聲......從啟示石塔傳來......這怎麼可能......？！", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#4$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那口鐘從來沒有響過啊？！", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#4$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......只在，只在......", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#7$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "數千年前，初代聖徒還行走於地上的時代。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#7$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“日間，薩科塔見天上烏黑，不見太陽。夜間，魔鬼的軍兵追來，戕害眾多薩科塔。薩科塔失去許多輝光。”", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......“眾聖徒說：跟隨我。於是石塔矗立。眾聖徒說：聆聽我。於是鐘聲鳴響。”", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g9_laterano_street", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“鐘聲回蕩在曠野，薩科塔便結成一心。”", "name": "激動的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_365_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“這是啟示，這是箴言。”", "name": "虔誠的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_365_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“日間便有亮光，不再被遮擋。”", "name": "激動的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_365_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“眾聖徒說：建築一座城市，乃是薩科塔的樂園。”", "name": "虔誠的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_365_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“眾聖徒說：這城該叫拉特蘭。”", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_357_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......怎麼會......", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#7$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啟示石塔是拉特蘭最古老的建築之一，不，如果按典籍所載，是先有啟示石塔，再有拉特蘭。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_357_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而聖鐘於此刻再度響起......", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為我們的小塞茜莉亞。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#7$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g4_laterano_cathedralliving", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可，為什麼......", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#7$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許那位無形的巨人音樂家想要寫幾個強音，看上了拉特蘭的老鐘，在配器時選中它。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "樞機薇爾麗芙，此刻在這聖堂中的卻是你我，不知是幸運，還是不幸。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......教宗閣下，我們必須立刻查清聖鐘鳴響的原因......不，不論是什麼原因，給出這個原因、解釋這個原因的......必須是教廷。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正值諸國使節齊聚拉特蘭，出席代表皆為見證者，這未嘗不是個機會。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去吧，薇爾麗芙，曉諭諸使節，拉特蘭的鐘聲數千年後再度響起，這是變革的預兆，我們必須聯合，為將來做好準備。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那啟示石塔......？", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等待已經足夠了，就開始工作吧。", "name": "教宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g9_laterano_street", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_357_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先導，您......難道早就知道了？塞茜莉亞到底是什麼人......她，她雖然是混血，但......難道還有什麼隱藏的秘密？", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#7$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，怎麼可能。她只是你我所知的塞茜莉亞而已，或許身世有一點特別，但並無玄奧隱秘。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許只是，拉特蘭本身都在渴求改變，塞茜莉亞......剛好遭遇了這個時刻。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又或者，她真是那個能夠彌平薩卡茲和薩科塔千年裂痕的人，以至於啟示為她而降，聖鐘為她而鳴。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，也有可能只是個誤會，是個巧合，是個埋藏在歷史中的黑色幽默。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們都知道，真相從來不是最重要的。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_357_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......不管怎樣，這給了我們機會。要我說，這未嘗不是我們被眷顧的證明。", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#2$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_357_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "教廷的精力現在應該都放在了使節區和啟示石塔那邊......", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_357_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們會為您鋪就那條路。您只需向前。", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......安多恩，鐘聲響了。", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那鐘聲屬於一個即將啟程的孩子。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎。", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的語氣很輕鬆，你決定了。", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的決定從未改變。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算會付出一切？", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算會付出一切。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這有意義嗎？", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "意義啊......意義不會憑空存在。我們的一切選擇，不過是構想它，塑造它，給它降臨的機會而已。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道了。", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "願你終能平靜。", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帕蒂亞，你剛才的那句話，有違我們的初衷。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人人皆為基石，我們所交疊夯築的坦途，留給後來者。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g2_laterano_cathedralhall", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "chara